cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

The paper deals with zero-shot and few-shot learning, which are subfields of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of semantic feature synthesis and competitive learning also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the mention of attribute vectors and data perturbation hints at a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
